# Facet-layout receipt, part 2: run on part 1's profile. A fresh process
# restores the graph from graph.json (position-free since S2) and re-dresses
# the layout from the arrangement.position facets — physics halted, so the
# capture must show part 1's settled arrangement, not a fresh spiral piled
# at the origin.
settle 40
key escape
assert nodes >= 15
assert visible
capture 01_layout_restored

log facet layout receipt part 2 complete
